#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:2
#: f984a45b27574b75a1356fb8b25b1503
msgid "蓝牙"
msgstr "Bluetooth"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:17
#: 36a1c96970d741cbb92935f0a6444801
msgid "WB2系列支持Bluetooth®LE 5.0 吗？"
msgstr "Does the WB2 series support Bluetooth® LE 5.0?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:18
#: 53d20b06ca8346179b12381c3d1ab9ed
msgid ""
"支持部分BLE 5.0功能，例如Channel Selection #2，Limited High Duty Cycle Non "
"Connectable Adv， 不支持LE Advertising Extension， 2M PHY，Long Range"
msgstr ""
"Some BLE 5.0 features are supported, such as Channel Selection #2 and "
"Limited High Duty Cycle Non Connectable Adv. LE Advertising Extension, 2M "
"PHY, and Long Range are not supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:24
#: be8f1bfa091f4f208150b247ccd06c7a
msgid "可以。蓝牙OTA协议为博流自研，支持断点续传，单次写flash大小可配置。"
msgstr ""
"Yes. The Bluetooth OTA protocol is developed by Bouffalo Lab. It supports "
"breakpoint resume, and the flash write size per operation is configurable."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:28
#: 6df4004a46b247849d5e1b808221711c
msgid "WB2系列的Bluetooth®LE 吞吐量是多少？"
msgstr "What is the Bluetooth® LE throughput of the WB2 series?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:29
#: 131351a368ac452494381f16b6c024f6
msgid ""
"两个模组之间进行吞吐量测试，BLE连接间隔设置为25ms，实测平均速率为570kbps 模组"
"与手机（mate30 pro）之间进行吞吐量测试，手机app使用BLE调试助手，BLE连接间隔设"
"置为25ms，实测平均速率为400kbps"
msgstr ""
"In a throughput test between two modules, with the BLE connection interval "
"set to 25 ms, the measured average rate was 570 kbps. In a throughput test "
"between the module and a mobile phone (Mate30 Pro), using the BLE Debug "
"Assistant app on the phone and with the BLE connection interval set to 25 "
"ms, the measured average rate was 400 kbps."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:33
#: 5313e4b019b34df584905742c1b81369
msgid "WB2系列的发射功率是多少？"
msgstr "What is the transmit power of the WB2 series?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:34
#: d620fcbbc3504bc7a5250624fe145348
msgid "支持0到15dBm"
msgstr "0 to 15 dBm is supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:37
#: 9f7b50d9fd224c21b208f51c54e8f020
msgid "WB2系列支持多少个客户端连接？"
msgstr "How many client connections does the WB2 series support?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:38
#: 2c05220d65f74983a71e593c84207ca2
msgid "最大可支持10个蓝牙连接，不局限于蓝牙设备类型（master或slave）。"
msgstr ""
"Up to 10 Bluetooth connections are supported, regardless of Bluetooth device "
"type (master or slave)."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:41
#: c9378e2fba154447939f5a263e0e54e1
msgid "Ai-WB2-12F模块可以连接手机放音乐吗"
msgstr "Can the Ai-WB2-12F module connect to a phone to play music?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:42
#: 1dd7197700c0483abc1a7a1351685621
msgid "不可以，因为使用的蓝牙是BLE蓝牙，无法传输音频数据。"
msgstr "No. The module uses BLE Bluetooth, which cannot transmit audio data."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:45
#: a7c056db58e64bb0af923cd965d3f4c3
msgid "为什么我写的ble组件，无法正常工作？"
msgstr "Why does the BLE component I wrote fail to work properly?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:46
#: 2b7b67a2a65d491c8251374d7b7f8772
msgid "经仔细检查，发现初始化遗漏了bl_sys_init"
msgstr ""
"After careful checking, it was found that bl_sys_init was missing during "
"initialization."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:49
#: 5fe2c85f3538439e80eb8ce4c22dbba6
msgid "蓝牙4.0的手机能连上WB2系列模组吗"
msgstr "Can a Bluetooth 4.0 phone connect to a WB2 series module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:50
#: 6d3759de7c7944028594b7b1f3e5b9a0
msgid "可以，手机端安装BLE蓝牙调试APP即可连接"
msgstr "Yes. Install a BLE Bluetooth debugging app on the phone to connect."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:53
#: 1986569d304f4fe695073602db6dfe22
msgid "请问一下Ai-WB2-12F模组的蓝牙是只能用来配网的吗？是否可以蓝牙控制？"
msgstr ""
"Is the Bluetooth function of the Ai-WB2-12F module only used for network "
"provisioning? Can it be used for Bluetooth control?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:54
#: 27abe6f65de24709b9259cb930a632ce
msgid "该模组的蓝牙可与手机APP中的蓝牙实现数据透传；"
msgstr ""
"The Bluetooth function of this module can implement data transparent "
"transmission with Bluetooth in a mobile app."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:57
#: 97e5715bbf8a4063b2f4226f3d016aca
msgid "请问Ai-WB2-12F-Kit配置蓝牙之后重启是否会保存配置项"
msgstr ""
"Will the Ai-WB2-12F-Kit save configuration items after Bluetooth is "
"configured and the device is restarted?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:58
#: 834010f56b2047338fdf6bfba0f68bfe
msgid "不会，每次重启需重新配置"
msgstr "No. It needs to be reconfigured after each restart."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:61
#: 797e3d6ea3eb4491b3145d92b674ac11
msgid "WB2系列模块支持蓝牙A2DP功能吗"
msgstr "Does the WB2 series module support Bluetooth A2DP?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:62
#: f598276e8bed499fb116e8eeb8574e4c
msgid "该功能为经典蓝牙功能，目前模块使用为BLE蓝牙，不支持蓝牙A2DP"
msgstr ""
"This is a Classic Bluetooth feature. The current module uses BLE Bluetooth "
"and does not support Bluetooth A2DP."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:65
#: 391f581ce4894977badd3105d87d28a4
msgid "WB2系列模块可以修改蓝牙MAC地址吗"
msgstr "Can the Bluetooth MAC address of the WB2 series module be modified?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:66
#: cd6f565dcfd74208ac4a5c2941622bd5
msgid "可以修改，AT指令和二次开发有相关的教程"
msgstr ""
"Yes. Related tutorials are available for both AT commands and secondary "
"development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:69
#: fa8cd0e66b964b36844ee2b9681e4cfe
msgid "请问为何Ai-WB2-12F模组实现蓝牙配网功能老是出现重启的现象呢？"
msgstr ""
"Why does the Ai-WB2-12F module keep restarting when implementing Bluetooth "
"network provisioning?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:70
#: c32e9c5fe1c3434d91a63e516ee8726c
msgid "检查一下模组供电情况，供电不足将导致模组重启；"
msgstr ""
"Check the module power supply. Insufficient power supply will cause the "
"module to restart."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:73
#: 78324f54add84f0b995974352b705cc7
msgid "WB2-12F蓝牙可以关闭吗"
msgstr "Can Bluetooth on the WB2-12F be turned off?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:74
#: c1307b44eb014548aa28d4cba4e935ea
msgid "默认蓝牙功能处于关闭状态"
msgstr "The Bluetooth function is disabled by default."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:77
#: 13c3b4671b614a31a16db71c46b8ff89
msgid "请问WB2-12F模组蓝牙支持2M速率传输么？"
msgstr "Does the WB2-12F module support 2M Bluetooth rate transmission?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:78
#: f026fb50cf614be3a43c9532d236ca5d
msgid "不支持；"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:81
#: 6b9c262e83f6460a91a8deb001e783cc
msgid "请问WB2-32S模组可以通过蓝牙获取手机APP的歌词么？"
msgstr "Can the WB2-32S module obtain lyrics from a mobile app via Bluetooth?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/ble-bt.rst:82
#: 34e050966699494f825b951ef8d1f146
msgid "不支持。"
msgstr "No."
